      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Workflow A — Book Indexer\n\nRun manually after dropping PDFs into your Drive books folder. Detects chapter boundaries with Claude Haiku and appends one row per book to `book_manifest`.\n\n**Sheet columns:** `drive_file_id | title | author | total_chapters | chapters_covered | chapter_boundaries_json | last_used_at | status | notes | indexed_at`",
